item.title: CVE-2023-5349|2023-10-30T20:27:59.972Z -- n%2Fa -- rmagick
item.description: A memory leak flaw was found in ruby-magick, an interface between Ruby and ImageMagick. This issue can lead to a denial of service (DOS) by memory exhaustion.
